<section class="about">
    <div class="section-header">
        <h2>About Us</h2>
        <p>Who We Are</p>
    </div>
    <div class="container about-contianer">
        <div class="about-left">
            <img src="~/Img/about.png" />
        </div>
        <div class="about-right">
            <h1>Empowering Minds, Transforming Futures</h1>
            <p>
                At EduConnect, we're dedicated to revolutionizing the way students connect with tutors. Our mission is to empower learners of all ages and backgrounds by providing access to high-quality, personalized education from the comfort of their own homes. Our platform brings together a diverse community of passionate tutors who are experts in their fields. Whether you're seeking help with mathematics, languages, sciences, or any other subject, we've got you covered.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="features">
    <div class="section-header">
        <h2>Features</h2>
        <p>What We Provide</p>
    </div>
    <div class="container features-container">
        <div class="feature">
            <h2>All Educational Domains</h2>
            <p>We serve all educational boards & kindergarten, primary, secondary, college, & university levels. We excel in tutoring Edexcel, IGCSE, and O/ A-level (Oxford/ Cambridge) with tuition at home & online tutoring in Pakistan. Join us for national & international test preparation; IELTS, GMAT, GAT, SAT, etc.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature">
            <h2>Pakistan-wide Services</h2>
            <p>We are available all over the country for online and home tuition services in Pakistan and have tutored millions of students. Get connected with expert teachers at affordable rates. We offer services in Islamabad, Rawalpindi, Lahore, Karachi, and other major cities.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature">
            <h2>Personalized tutoring</h2>
            <p>We have been in terms of online tuition and home tutor services in Pakistan for several years. Our experience convinces us that every kid’s strengths and weaknesses vary. Therefore, emphasizing individual attention, we provide personalized tutoring experiences for every student.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature">
            <h2>Goal-driven teachers</h2>
            <p>We have honest, time-committed, cost-efficient, prestigious institutions-qualified tutors abiding by all the teaching ethics. Our teachers help students achieve their dream grades. Besides that, they also boost students’ creativity to grasp complicated concepts in future studies.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature">
            <h2>Flexibility guaranteed</h2>
            <p>We are flexible with lesson timings, days, and places to offer tutoring services at your convenience. You are free to choose how much you can pay and whom to work with. If you have a specific request, we go the extra mile to arrange it according to your preference.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature">
            <h2>Realistic approach</h2>
            <p>We are much more than a traditional tutoring service. Creating a solid foundation for students is what our online home tutoring services work for. We encourage the right education mindset and focus on developing a child’s full potential in learning.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>